Task 3: HTML Form Creation

Task Description:

Create an HTML form with the following requirements:

Fields:

Username: required, 5–20 characters, autofocus on page load.

Email: readonly, prefilled with o@o.com.

Token: hidden, value = b92f1fc2fce391ad7af633723afd3055.

Programming Skills Checkboxes:

User can select multiple skills: Problem Solving, Logical Thinking, Advanced Search, Analysis, Planning.

Each checkbox must have a label linked with for and id.

At least one skill must be checked by default.

All checkboxes must share the same name: skills.

Job Role Radio Buttons:

User can select only one option: Front-End Developer, Back-End Developer, Business Analyst, Project Manager, Scrum Master.

Each radio button must have a label linked with for and id.

At least one option must be checked by default.

All radio buttons must share the same name: job.

Programming Language Dropdown:

A <select> element containing programming languages with versions.

Example groups: PHP (v5.0, v7.0, v8.0), Python (v2.0, v3.0, v3.9), JavaScript (ES5, ES6, ESNext).

User can select one language only.

Name of the select: language.

Brief Textarea:

Name: brief.

Should contain a prefilled text and a placeholder: "Write Here Why You Want To Learn Programming".

Buttons:

Reset button labeled "Empty" → clears user input.

Submit button labeled "Send" → submits data using GET method.

Additional Requirements:

All labels must be properly linked to inputs so clicking the label activates the input.

The submitted data should appear in the URL after submission
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Task 3 Form Solution</title>
</head>
<body>
  <form method="get">

    <!-- Username -->
    <label for="username">Username</label><br>
    <input type="text" id="username" name="Username" autofocus minlength="5" maxlength="20" required>
    <br><hr>

    <!-- Email -->
    <label for="email">Email</label><br>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="Email" readonly value="o@o.com">
    <br><hr>

    <!-- Hidden Token -->
    <input type="hidden" name="Token" value="b92f1fc2fce391ad7af633723afd3055">

    <!-- Programming Skills Checkboxes -->
    <label>Programming Skills</label><br>
    <input type="checkbox" id="ps" name="skills" value="Problem Solving" checked>
    <label for="ps">Problem Solving</label><br>

    <input type="checkbox" id="lt" name="skills" value="Logical Thinking">
    <label for="lt">Logical Thinking</label><br>

    <input type="checkbox" id="as" name="skills" value="Advanced Search">
    <label for="as">Advanced Search</label><br>

    <input type="checkbox" id="an" name="skills" value="Analysis">
    <label for="an">Analysis</label><br>

    <input type="checkbox" id="pl" name="skills" value="Planning">
    <label for="pl">Planning</label>
    <hr>

    <!-- Job Role Radio Buttons -->
    <label>Job Role</label><br>

    <input type="radio" id="fe" name="job" value="Front-End Developer">
    <label for="fe">Front-End Developer</label><br>

    <input type="radio" id="be" name="job" value="Back-End Developer" checked>
    <label for="be">Back-End Developer</label><br>

    <input type="radio" id="ba" name="job" value="Business Analyst">
    <label for="ba">Business Analyst</label><br>

    <input type="radio" id="pm" name="job" value="Project Manager">
    <label for="pm">Project Manager</label><br>

    <input type="radio" id="sm" name="job" value="Scrum Master">
    <label for="sm">Scrum Master</label>
    <hr>

    <!-- Programming Languages Select -->
    <label for="language">Programming Language</label><br>
    <select name="language" id="language">
      <optgroup label="PHP">
        <option value="php5">v5.0</option>
        <option value="php7">v7.0</option>
        <option value="php8">v8.0</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="Python">
        <option value="python2">v2.0</option>
        <option value="python3">v3.0</option>
        <option value="python3.9">v3.9</option>
      </optgroup>
      <optgroup label="JavaScript">
        <option value="jsES5">ES5</option>
        <option value="jsES6">ES6</option>
        <option value="jsESNext">ESNext</option>
      </optgroup>
    </select>
    <hr>

    <!-- Brief Textarea -->
    <label for="brief">Brief</label><br>
    <textarea name="brief" id="brief" cols="50" rows="10" placeholder="Write Here Why You Want To Learn Programming">Write Here Why You Want To Learn Programming</textarea>
    <hr>

    <!-- Buttons -->
    <input type="reset" value="Empty">
    <input type="submit" value="Send">

  </form>
</body>
</html>
